{"tid":1288922,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廣東省規劃：粵港澳3年內設信用評分制度","createTime":"2019-07-05T23:51:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T01:08:54.000Z","uid":186071,"like":0,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c0d09126da27602059994d01e417b0b7d8cefdfd","tid":1288922,"uid":186071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T23:51:10.000Z","msg":"【廣東省規劃：粵港澳3年內設信用評分制度】<br />\n【學者：香港實施有難度 牽涉港人資料機會微】<br />\n<br />\n廣東省近日正式提出粵港澳大灣區未來三年的行動計劃，其中一點提到要建立信用評分制度，香港和澳門都有份。計劃指，廣東省要和港澳共享信用信息，對企業實施信用獎勵和懲罰措施。<br />\n<br />\n有學者指，共享信息只是第一步，但由於三地政制有別，要在香港實施信用評分制度有難度。他估計會被共享的暫時都只是內地的黑名單資料，不會牽涉到香港市民。<br />\n<br />\n計劃亦提到，要推動內地和港澳信息互通，包括實時監測和應急處置工作等；三地亦將會加強警務合作交流，不定期演練，統籌應對傳統和非傳統的安全威脅。<br />\n<br />\n#粵港澳大灣區<br />\n#信用評分制度<br />\n#警務合作<br />\n#有線中國組<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/265944843550009/posts/2179325322211942?s=596136172&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=xmo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F265944843550009%2Fposts%2F2179325322211942%3Fs%3D596136172%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dxmo&d=TgwWsw16K2C65RuBgL3vHfkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=ceed7f96\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/265944843550009/posts/2179325322211942?s=596136172&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=xmo</a>"},{"pid":"abd59594f1a294e36e4d40dbffb7ab3d5545d0e4","tid":1288922,"uid":2267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T23:59:09.000Z","msg":"黐撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"615b0420b4b1d9b8a7092421d7f095f61e97657f","tid":1288922,"uid":2864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T01:06:23.000Z","msg":"夠膽咪宜家推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c86354b10ccbab12d887011877ec4fb7e563d368","tid":1288922,"uid":53172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"